{"tid":744601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「爸爸銀行」免費出租臨時爸爸　給單親家庭小朋友一點溫暖","createTime":"2018-07-16T05:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T06:12:04.000Z","uid":20815,"like":203,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"9affd76862336c28f95f826a469f6b40312a1bc7","tid":744601,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/japan_thumb_20180710_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2Fjapan_thumb_20180710_ch_1024.jpg&h=54809a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本最近出現了「爸爸銀行」，免費出租爸爸，代陪單親孩子玩樂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現代人工作忙碌，經常無暇陪伴孩子，對一些身兼父職的單親媽媽來説，既要兼顧工作，又要照顧孩子，便更是吃力。日本最近就出現了「爸爸銀行」，為有需要的家庭提供「臨時爸爸」的服務。<br />\n<br />\n「爸爸銀行」供喜歡照顧小孩的男士報名，他們大多都擅長DIY、烹飪、玩紙板等不同活動。在網站註冊後，他們會被編入「爸爸圖鑒」，家長可通過Facebook等平台委託他們幫忙，由於「臨時爸爸」的是義工性質，因此費用全免。<br />\n<br />\n「臨時爸爸」的服務多元，包括在家陪伴孩子畫畫、帶孩子到戶外玩樂、參加學校運動會為孩子打氣、出席家長會等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/22728767_817042531799943_457451155956200563_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F22728767_817042531799943_457451155956200563_n_1024.jpg&h=0087327c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與小朋友去長野縣一起登山。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/22730351_817042635133266_4477977880468082047_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F22730351_817042635133266_4477977880468082047_n_1024.jpg&h=f4ed75c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和孩子觀賞風景。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/36350003_943975992439929_4374303489510080512_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F36350003_943975992439929_4374303489510080512_n_1024.jpg&h=a40b400e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附近有大自然環境、聽着蟲叫及流水聲，與小朋友舒服地玩樂，像活在烏托邦的世界。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男保姆需求亦增<br />\n<br />\n除了「臨時爸爸」，日本對男保姆的需求也越來越高。30歲的男保姆吉野一真平時是一名格鬥家和教練，他喜歡戶外活動，因此經常陪孩子爬樹、玩躲避球、籃球、到野外露營。男保姆的出現，亦解決了父母無暇陪伴孩子玩樂的難題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2108503/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2108503%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=OBl%2FAhGcvaNzpESIBU6PjARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e1e693db\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2108503/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"95e03777b7479946aff35372ed8a9695c2b72aec","tid":744601,"uid":20815,"like":598,"dislike":6,"score":592,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"成件事好溫馨好正氣，但我成個腦都係&quot;pt老公&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f537bf0b8e849ee5cd7d40a5487a9f4f9f79dba","tid":744601,"uid":63909,"like":384,"dislike":4,"score":380,"quote":{"pid":"95e03777b7479946aff35372ed8a9695c2b72aec","tid":744601,"uid":20815,"like":598,"dislike":6,"score":592,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"成件事好溫馨好正氣，但我成個腦都係&quot;pt老公&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"地方的媽媽需要"},{"pid":"cffa7485ffbee5d168a65d2eaee98d59ff6b6916","tid":744601,"uid":15,"like":300,"dislike":4,"score":296,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"分分鐘可以食埋個人妻"},{"pid":"3f7dc63a0e02c918f04a026515b500b566a9f73c","tid":744601,"uid":20815,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"quote":{"pid":"4f537bf0b8e849ee5cd7d40a5487a9f4f9f79dba","tid":744601,"uid":63909,"like":384,"dislike":4,"score":380,"quote":{"pid":"95e03777b7479946aff35372ed8a9695c2b72aec","tid":744601,"uid":20815,"like":598,"dislike":6,"score":592,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"成件事好溫馨好正氣，但我成個腦都係&qu